{"tid":616411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［求饒］泛民：再次重申堅持反港獨，討論港獨不同於鼓吹港獨！","createTime":"2018-04-04T07:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T07:16:58.000Z","uid":49388,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ad4cbfe3ff17c11c6e6bb959975b784c55776f57","tid":616411,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T07:10:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/145904_812a3212cc2b90b1ec637a45f47b8476.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F145904_812a3212cc2b90b1ec637a45f47b8476.png&h=cb3e8204&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n解讀：<br />\n泛民：阿爺希望你放心不用怕，其實我地民主派都一致認同鼓吹港獨是不道德甚至犯法，載教授只是衝口而出説希望作出討論，並無冒犯祖國之意。我們泛民一直堅持商量態度，並一致堅持打著鮮明旗幟反香港獨立，望中央人民政府諒解。"},{"pid":"2a85b322a7aa819ce55dcc45be807e0e612d6c2c","tid":616411,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T07:16:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}